data.description: Cheesesteaks, Soft Pretzels, Wooder Ice, Best Sports Fans, and 213 Overlook Rd. These are all things Philly! Come take a look at this house, which is tucked away on a cul-de-sac, meaning you have no through traffic on the street. As you enter, you notice the hardwood floors, that are throughout the main and second level. The living room is great for relaxing or watching TV. Sit and enjoy that morning cup of coffee or evening dinner in the dining room.  Whether making toast or a gourmet dinner, the kitchen is the place to make it happen. Head upstairs and you will find two bedrooms, both with ceiling fans. A full bath completes this floor. Walk downstairs to the large basement. Here you’ll find space to create an office, gym or whatever you may want.  You have plenty of additional space for storage. From the basement, step outside to your fenced in backyard. Here you can hang out with friends, BBQ (no matter what the season) or just simply enjoy being outside. Now is the time to get your very own Philly Special!
